metadata.name: Top Unique Screen Views (excl. Home/Welcome)
metadata.description: HPX Events Model with IIDE Table

datasets.name: paas_tracking_card_metrics
datasets.query: SELECT DATE_TRUNC('day', session_start_date_time) AS day_event_date_time, app_name AS screen, COUNT(DISTINCT session_id) AS unique_screen_views FROM team_css_analytics_prod.hpx_analytics.paas_tracking_card_metrics WHERE session_start_date_time >= '2023-05-01' AND app_name NOT IN ('home', 'welcome', 'welcomecontainer', 'welcome-core', 'support') GROUP BY DATE_TRUNC('day', session_start_date_time), app_name ORDER BY day_event_date_time, unique_screen_views DESC

frame.title: Top Unique Screen Views (excl. Home/Welcome) Over Time
